<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />We have become a reproach for our neighbors,</para>

<para style="q1">mocking and derision to those who are around us.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />How long, Yahweh? Will you stay angry forever?</para>

<para style="q1">How long will your jealous anger burn like fire?</para>
